gdt.data.grain

Class Identity

  • java.lang.Object
    • gdt.data.grain.Identity
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Sack

    public class Identity
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents non-specific object having unique identifier. An identity structure has two string fields: key - the unique identifier path - the path of the file where the identity is stored. The path can be null.
